General.Name: Global UAV Technologies Ltd
General.Description: Global UAV Technologies Ltd. operates as a technology company that offers unmanned aerial vehicle (UAV) services in Canada. It offers aerial surveys, high eye aerial imaging, and UAV regulatory services, as well as UAV-based surface and sub-surface imagery services for various technical fields, including mining and aggregates, agriculture, inspection, and construction surveying. The company was formerly known as Alta Vista Ventures Ltd. and changed its name to Global UAV Technologies Ltd. in May 2017. Global UAV Technologies Ltd. is based in Vancouver, Canada.
